The version of normliz.lib requires version 3.10.0 or nweer of Normaliz.

The documentation normaliz.pdfcan still be used, but it does not contain the new functions
that come with this version. For the time being, open normaliz.lib with
your favorite editor, read the introduction and the information of the procedures that
you are intereseted in.

As a first test run

    Singular basic_test.sing

and then

    Singular extended_test.sing

These scripts require that the binary normaliz is in your search path for executable files.

If you are interested in Sagbi bases, sagbiNormaliz.lib may be useful for you. Use this file is a preliminary documentation.

